## 7.4.2 Across Time of Day

### Purpose
This subsection studies intraday variation in price impact.

### Setup / formulation
The chapter compares:

- static monthly fitting;
- non-parametric time-of-day fitting.

The non-parametric method fits different model parameters by time-of-day interval.

Intervals used:

- $90$-minute intervals for $h=1$ minute;
