## Key formulas to preserve

- Bin return:

$$
r_t = \frac{P_{t+\delta t}}{P_t} - 1.
$$

- Market activity state:

$$
v_{t+\delta t} - v_t = -\beta v_t \delta t + |q_t|.
$$

- Horizon return:

$$
\Delta_t^h P = \frac{P_{t+h}}{P_t} - 1.
$$

- Horizon impact increment:

$$
\Delta_t^h I = I_{t+h} - I_t.
$$

- Impact regression:

$$
\Delta^h P = \Delta^h I + \epsilon.
$$

- Alpha prediction of unperturbed price:

$$
\alpha_t^h =
\mathbb{E}\left[
\frac{S_{t+h}}{S_t} - 1
\mid \mathcal{F}_t
\right].
$$

- OFI model:

$$
I_{t+h} - I_t
=
\lambda \sigma
\sum_{s=t}^{t+h-\delta t}
\frac{\mathrm{ofi}_s}{ADV}.
$$

- OW model:

$$
I_{t+\delta t} - I_t
=
-\beta I_t \delta t
+
\lambda \sigma \frac{q_t}{ADV}.
$$

- Locally concave Bouchaud model:

$$
I_{t+\delta t} - I_t
=
-\beta I_t \delta t
+
\lambda \sigma \operatorname{sign}(q_t)
\sqrt{\frac{|q_t|}{ADV}}.
$$

- Reduced-form model:

$$
I_{t+\delta t} - I_t
=
-\beta I_t \delta t
+
\frac{\lambda \sigma q_t}{\sqrt{ADV \cdot v_t}}.
$$

- AFS latent state:

$$
J_{t+\delta t} - J_t
=
-\beta J_t \delta t
+
\frac{q_t}{ADV}.
$$

- AFS impact:

$$
I_t
=
\lambda \sigma \operatorname{sign}(J_t)\sqrt{|J_t|}.
$$

- Model $t$-stat:

$$
\frac{\operatorname{mean}(\hat{\lambda})}{\operatorname{sd}(\hat{\lambda})}.
$$

- End-of-day imbalance proxy:

$$
\mathrm{imb}
=
\frac{\sum_t q_t}{\sum_t |q_t|}.
$$

- Transaction costs:

$$
TC
=
\int_0^T I_t \, dQ_t
+
\frac{1}{2}[I,Q]_T.
$$

- Position inflation:

$$
F_T = I_T Q_T.
$$

- Pairwise cross-impact counterfactual:

$$
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid do(Q_i)].
$$

- Back-door adjustment under $\mathcal{C}$:

$$
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid do(Q_i)]
=
\int
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid Q_i,\bar S=s]
p(\bar S=s)
\, ds.
$$

- Factor-mediated stock-level cross-impact:

$$
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid do(\bar Q)].
$$

- Factor-level cross-impact:

$$
\mathbb{E}[\Delta \bar P \mid do(\bar Q)].
$$

- Factor model adjustment under flow confounding:

$$
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid do(\Delta \bar P)]
=
\int
\mathbb{E}[\Delta P_j \mid \Delta \bar P,\bar Q=q]
p(\bar Q=q)
\, dq.
$$

